# Unicode.GeneralCategory.letterNumber

**Case**

A letter-like numeric character.

## Declaration

```swift
case letterNumber
```

## Discussion

This value corresponds to the category `Letter_Number` (abbreviated `Nl`) in the [https://unicode.org/reports/tr44/#General_Category_Values].
